				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Well Oorscaat, you can argue all you want for the necro, and flame as many class pages as you want with your nonsense, but all anyone has to do is check the PvP server stats at everlore.com to see that Necros suck at PvP. Wizards, Druids, Magicians, and Rangers top it all the time. A Necro seldom even appears on any of the subcategory charts, let alone the main top 10. Check it out if you doubt it. Necros are &quot;ok&quot; at solo, but that's the best and only aspect to playing one. But honestly, and this is jusy MY opinion, I solo just fine with everyone of my characters. Even above level 30. So really, with that fact, and MY experience with the type of people who play necros (the children who flame other class pages with sheer nonsense about necros being the best at everything in the game), I see no reason why anyone should even play one.<BR>
